Package org.bukkit.block.data.type

Interface TurtleEgg

All Superinterfaces:
BlockData, Cloneable
public interface TurtleEgg
extends BlockData
'hatch' is the number of turtles which may hatch from these eggs.
'eggs' is the number of eggs which appear in this block.
